            <p>View scripts are not intended to be accessed directly via the browser; they are to be consumed by Zend_View, at which time they run within an instance of Zend_View and $this is populated. Follow the instructions in the quick start, and setup a virtual host pointing to the application's "public" directory, and then access <a href="http://yourhostname/guestbook">http://yourhostname/guestbook</a> -- which will then display the correct output.</p>

